Package com.github.bwsoft.iris.message

To compose or parse a structured message containing fields, repeating groups, or nested repeating groups.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Field
    The definition of a message field.
    FieldHeader
    Defines a header for a field
    Group
    A group is a special field that contains other fields and/or nested groups.
    GroupObject
    A GroupObject is a section in a message that is defined by a group.
    GroupObjectArray
    A GroupObjectArray is a section in a message that contains several repeated identical structures.
    Message
    A message is a special Group without a parent.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SBEMessageSchema
    A factory class to create SBE messages within a scope of a message schema.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FieldType
    Defines all supported types.
